dcterms:description: A multilingual dataset consisting of training and testing sets for English, German, and Spanish, as well as a French test set for cross-lingual complex word identification. The dataset was annotated by native and non-native speakers to identify words that may be difficult for non-native speakers.
dcterms:title: English Dataset
